         <OBJECT_CONTRACT>
            <TITLE>
               <P>Tune into Tourism</P>
            </TITLE>
            <REFERENCE_NUMBER>OJE 0168</REFERENCE_NUMBER>
            <CPV_MAIN>
               <CPV_CODE CODE="79340000"/>
            </CPV_MAIN>
            <TYPE_CONTRACT CTYPE="SERVICES"/>
            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>Highlands and Islands Enterprise are looking for a supplier with a creative outlook to work with them to deliver the “Tune into Tourism” programme. The supplier will require a range of technical services and expertise whilst offering best value in the expenditure of public funds. The duration of this contract is 2 years with the option to extend for a further 2 x 1 year periods.</P>
            </SHORT_DESCR>
            <VAL_ESTIMATED_TOTAL CURRENCY="GBP">308000</VAL_ESTIMATED_TOTAL>
            <NO_LOT_DIVISION/>
            <OBJECT_DESCR ITEM="1">
               <CPV_ADDITIONAL>
                  <CPV_CODE CODE="92110000"/>
               </CPV_ADDITIONAL>
               <CPV_ADDITIONAL>
                  <CPV_CODE CODE="92100000"/>
               </CPV_ADDITIONAL>
               <CPV_ADDITIONAL>
                  <CPV_CODE CODE="32210000"/>
               </CPV_ADDITIONAL>
               <CPV_ADDITIONAL>
                  <CPV_CODE CODE="32000000"/>
               </CPV_ADDITIONAL>
               <CPV_ADDITIONAL>
                  <CPV_CODE CODE="38650000"/>
               </CPV_ADDITIONAL>
               <n2016:NUTS CODE="UKM6"/>
               <SHORT_DESCR>
                  <P>Highlands and Islands Enterprise are looking to appoint a suitably qualified supplier to work with them to deliver the Tune into Tourism Programme. The purpose of the programme is to enable businesses to:</P>
                  <P>— learn about the latest trends from subject experts and industry contributors,</P>
                  <P>— identify areas within their business that could benefit from innovative action,</P>
                  <P>— hear what other businesses have successfully done to maximise business opportunities.</P>
                  <P>The successful supplier shall be required to provide the following services (which are not exhaustive) as appropriate:</P>
                  <P>Produce Webinars that provide an interactive experience for online viewers. Produce Short video podcast tutorials/talks that offer tourism businesses a range of practical business insights and tips that can be applied in their own operation. Produce Facebook Live sessions offering informal, friendly and personal observations drawn from interviews and experiences on agreed subjects.</P>
               </SHORT_DESCR>
               <AC_QUALITY>
                  <AC_CRITERION>Quality</AC_CRITERION>
                  <AC_WEIGHTING>70</AC_WEIGHTING>
               </AC_QUALITY>
               <AC_PRICE>
                  <AC_WEIGHTING>30</AC_WEIGHTING>
               </AC_PRICE>
               <VAL_OBJECT CURRENCY="GBP">308000</VAL_OBJECT>
               <DURATION TYPE="MONTH">24</DURATION>
               <RENEWAL/>
               <RENEWAL_DESCR>
                  <P>2 x 1 year extension periods</P>
               </RENEWAL_DESCR>
               <NO_ACCEPTED_VARIANTS/>
               <NO_OPTIONS/>
               <NO_EU_PROGR_RELATED/>
            </OBJECT_DESCR>
         </OBJECT_CONTRACT>
